OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be frequent showers
OL,6,Ftoday, merging into more general rain
OL,7,Fat times, with a chance of thunder.
OL,8,FTurning increasingly windy and
OL,9,Fgenerally on the cool side, though
OL,10,Ffeeling warmer in any sunshine and in
OL,11,Fsheltered spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing somewhat this
OL,14,Fevening and overnight, with some clear
OL,15,Fspells developing across the region
OL,16,Flater in the night. Winds slowly
OL,17,Feasing too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
