OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FMuch drier on Friday, though
OL,6,Fshowers are still likely in places.
OL,7,FVariable amounts of cloud with bright
OL,8,For sunny spells for many. Feeling cool
OL,9,Ffor the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,12,Fwindy at first on Saturday with rain,
OL,13,Feasing later. Bright spells and
OL,14,Fshowers on Sunday. Overnight rain
OL,15,Fclearing on Monday to sunny spells and
OL,16,Fshowers again. Near normal
OL,17,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
